data.description: Here is your opportunity to own one of the largest homes in the neighborhood without the huge price tag. This 4 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home is located in Talawanda SD and features nearly 3,000 finished sqft. with a walkout basement.  Build instant equity by replacing the carpet and adding a fresh coat of paint. You will love entertaining on the large deck overlooking the backyard.
